## ğŸ§  How the Game Works

1. Ball moves continuously across the screen.
2. Paddles move vertically based on keyboard input.
3. If the ball hits a paddle â†’ it bounces back.
4. If the ball misses a paddle â†’ opposite player scores.
5. Scoreboard updates instantly.

---

## ğŸ¯ Objective

Defend your side of the screen and score points on your opponent.
The game continues until you decide to stop playing.

